3. 

In these Regulations – 

“Act of 2018” means the Public Health (Alcohol) Act 2018 (No. 24 of 2018); 

“health information” means the information referred to in paragraphs (iv), (v) 
and (vi) of section 12(1) of the Act of 2018; 

“health symbol” means the symbol referred to in paragraph (2) of Regulation 5; 

“health warning” means a warning referred to in paragraph (1) or (3) of 
Regulation 5. 

